title: Astraware Solitaire v1.7.9 (Android) [DM] {AMRG}
description:
INFO:
Version: 1.7.9
Size : 22 MB
Developer: Astraware Limited
Language: English

DESCRIPTION:
12 of the most popular card games in 1 pack. Includes Klondike, Pyramid, Spider, Clock, Yukon, Canfield, Four Seasons, Sultan's Harem, Idiot's Delight, Golf, Calculation, and Freecell.
Each game has custom gameplay options which allow you to play using your favorite variation on the standard rules. Personalize your game with a choice of card fronts, decorative card backs, and beautiful game backgrounds. Astraware Solitaire also includes the fun Golden Trophy Deck awards system - get all 52 awards to collect the Golden Deck and unlock it to play with!
